                      <h4>Ramesh Behl</h4>
                      <p>Ramesh Behl exclusively worked with R.D. Burman for the music in all of his films, a testament to their strong professional rapport.</p>
                      <strong>Analysis:</strong>
                      <p>The Behl-Burman association resulted in diverse soundtracks ranging from intense drama to youthful romance. While less extensively documented in search results than the Nasir Hussain collaborations, these films consistently featured strong musical scores that were integral to Behl's storytelling.</p>

