							<h4>ğŸ¤£ Satte Pe Satta (1982)</h4>
							<p>For Babu, Boss has Annette Pinto gargle water into the mic to get that weird, spine-tingling soundâ€”equal parts creepy and comic. The brothersâ€™ harmonica theme becomes their identity.</p>

