			<span class="genius-song-block song-5">
				"Dhanno Ki Ankhon Mein (Kitaab, 1977)"
					Boss R.D. Burman conjures rustic magic here with rhythmic tabla and bongo duets that pulsate like a lively village heartbeat. The lively flute and accordion motifs create a colorful sonic tapestry. But wait, the true tech wizardry lies in the guitarâ€™s Flanger effectâ€”yes, our Boss was messing with guitar sounds back when it was rare! This gadget modulates the guitarâ€™s tone, bending it into otherworldly shapes, enriching the folk texture with an electrifying modern edge, brilliantly blending old and new.
