				"Pyar Humein Kis Mod Pe (Satte Pe Satta,1982)"
					This track brilliantly juxtaposes a slow, tender introduction with synthesizers and tabla gradually building into a vivacious celebration filled with cheering â€œee-yaaâ€ fun interjectionsâ€”signature of the Bossâ€™s playful approach to rhythms and moods. The blend of western electric guitars and Indian classical percussion is seamless, capturing loveâ€™s unpredictable and joyous turns with Kishore Kumar and Lata Mangeshkar dancing vocally in sync.
